##### WHY BarleyDB

Many times you want to use simple db functions to interact with your databse but when you start you have to program
exceptions, errors and more.. now you can include our BarleyDB library and forget it!


##### Improve the code

BarleyDB code is available on github, you can fork it and improve it :D This is only de base of any database access library

